		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In your new 2013-07-24 version: From the menu, if you hold the START or A button slightly too long, it will skip the next screen. Consider waiting for the button to be released before checking if it's down again.<br /><br />(For example, if you start the game, but hold the START button slightly too long, you skip over the level title screen. If you try to go to the password screen, but hold the A button slightly too long, it will start the game with the default password.)

		

